title: New basement rental
posting_body: ['We have a new basement apartment for rent in a really nice neighborhood in lawrenceville.', 'It is approx 1450 sq ft. Big full kitchen, new appliances, walk in pantry and lots of space for kitchen table etc.', 'it has a family room and living room with 2 bedrooms.', 'Spacious and light and very clean.', 'We are looking to rent to tenants who aren’t  easily bothered by noise, as we have 4 small children living above you.', 'We are also looking for quiet-ish tenants because we have small children that sleep early and need quiet.', 'Our requirements are to be very very clean and', 'Responsible and respectful tenants.', 'Give me a call or text for more details.', 'Thanks', 'Mina']
